The main page should have three sections at least. One for the AI automation section where it details all the things. And the other section is for the e-commerce partnerships where we deal in private label management, wholesale management, and selling on eBay, Amazon, Walmart. TikTok shop and these e-commerce marketplaces. We offer a partnership model where we only charge you from the share of the profits that we generate for you. That's the core value of our proposition. 

